Which deal sourcing channels generate the most opportunities? The answer varies by firm: younger PE firms managing smaller funds or investing in emerging markets tend to source more deals in-house, while firms executing large buyouts derive a smaller percentage from their proprietary networks.4 It should be added that sourcing deals in emerging markets adds to the complexity, as explained by our guest author below.

