EVOLUTION OF PRIVATE EQUITY




Welcome to the final chapter of our book. After laying the theoretical foundations and sharing industry best practice, we shift from the arm’s-length, factual style of the preceding 24 chapters to three distinct opinion pieces that address the past, present and future of private equity (PE), written in our respective voices. In addition to providing some much appreciated editorial license, our comments are designed to connect the dots, touch on some of the more controversial issues raised in both the media and public discourse and invite discussions related to the future of the PE industry.

